  "description": "CHARACTER STUDIO - made by AEiOU \u2014 offline WebGL2 character creation and premium browser machinima suite with reusable full-character Library assets, a frame-accurate nonlinear timeline, unified professional UI, layered stereo audio, portable media bundles, and configurable HD\u20134K WebM masters.",
